<br />

<br />
After some time off (pre-LDoN) I decided to start back up and make a bard this time around (got 65 necro, 61 monk, 55 shaman).  My question is, is the bard epic still worth the effort considering that there are (are there?) better weapons out there that are more easily obtainable?  Thanks in advance for any advice.</span></td>
