				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: epic still worth it?<a name="40293"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 17 04 1:13 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>There are better weapons in the sense that there are a lot of weapons with better dmg/delay ratios.  You need to hit VT, GoD, or the Elemental Planes to get a bard a weapon with better stats.
<br />

<br />
There is still NO weapon anywhere in the game that gives you the 5-way instrument bonus of the bard epic.  Check the magelos of time-guild bards and some still use it regularly.  Finding worn items and weapons with equal-or-better instrument bonuses built in so that you can bag the epic is not at all easy.</span></td>
